[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "２ｎｄライブ、お疲れさまでございました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00381",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "打ち上げのために、食事を取り寄せましたわ。\n好きなだけ食べてくださいまし！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00382",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "社長殿～！　ありがたき幸せにございます～！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00383",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "わ、私もお呼ばれしてしまって\nよろしかったのでしょうか……！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00384",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "もちろんですわ。あなたの錬金術による演出……\nわたくし大いに感動いたしました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00385",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ララ・プロダクション代表として、あなたとは\nぜひ今後とも良いお付き合いをしていければと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00386",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "きょ、恐縮ですっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00387",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ライブお疲れさま！\nお客さん、たくさん来てたね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00388",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ええ。決して多くはなかったけれど――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00389",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "あんたの提案のおかげかもね。\n１ｓｔライブはたったの三人だったのに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00390",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "みんなでビラ配り頑張ったもんね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00391",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "この調子なら、５ｔｈライブには\n広場に入りきらないくらいのお客さんが集まるかも！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00392",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "調子に乗ってんじゃないわよ。\nアイドルはここからが大変なのよ。ね、リーダー？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00393",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……ん？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00394",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "アイドル活動はここからが大変なんだって\nイザナに言ってやってよ、リーダー",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00395",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "せ、拙者がリーダーでございますか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00396",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "そうでしょ。私たちのことまとめてくれてるし、\nライブでのМＣも様になっていたし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00397",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "うん！　ヨハナより鬼門がリーダーに向いてるって\nハンマーも言ってるよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00398",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "はぁ！？　生意気なハンマーね。\n切り刻んでやるから貸しなさい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00399",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ダメーっ！　ハンマーいじめ反対！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00400",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "こら二人とも！\n食事の席なのだから、暴れてはならぬ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00401",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふふ。三人とも、\nまた一段と仲良くなれたようですわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00402",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "さ、皆さん。\nちょっと真面目な話をいたしますわよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00403",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "皆さんの働きもあり、２ｎｄライブの客足は\n１ｓｔライブを大きく上回る結果となりました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00404",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "であれば。より大規模なライブを目指したい。\nそう思うのは必然ですわよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00405",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "そうね。いつまでも路上ライブじゃ\n世界一のアイドルにはほど遠いわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00406",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "でもより大規模なライブって？\n王都の広場より広い所を用意するの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00407",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "規模というのは、広さだけを表すものではありませんわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00408",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あなたたちには、多くのアーティストが集まる\nとあるライブへの出演を目指してもらいます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00409",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "毎年、年末に王都で行われる大規模フェス――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00410",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ま、まさか！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00411",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "――『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』の次なる目標は、\nカウントダウンフェスですわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00412",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]